cast.overview: Fresh off an almost career-ending accident, stuntman Colt Seavers has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job.
cast.title: The Fall Guy

details.biography:
Alex Lee is a comedian, television presenter and actor with a background in journalism.

Alex’s television credits include ABC TV’s The Checkout, The Chaser’s Election Desk, The Roast, Media Circus, Story Club, Saturday Night Rove, SBS’ The Feed and Stan‘s The Other Guy.
details.name: Alex Lee
